info: Rating, 5 stars,  · July 2019,  · Stayed one night
rating_comment: Amazing stay! The place is super clean, very comfortable, well decorated, and quiet. Perfect for a weekend getaway or a long trip. And value for money is terrific!

This was an excellent place located in a posh locality of Uttara, Dhaka with all the amenities and markets located at a stone throw's distance from the property. The host helped us out of the way in taking us to the nearby markets and attractions. They have a cab of their own which you can rent for your travel around the city with an amicable driver. All in all a great place and a great stay and overall a great hospitable behaviour from Bangladeshi people. Loved it completely !!

Best location and one of the best apartment to stay in uttara. If you are not obsessed by Gulshan or Banani then this is a perfect place. Prime location with all desirable amenities nearby and secured well. Mr. Shumon was a delightful to interact with specially if you are health conscious. Care taker Khaled is a charm he can understand and speak hindi well which is an advantage for Indians. Though I didn't used but car is there with driver always available. Perfectly a thumbs up....go without a blink..... Will surely be my only stop in dhaka now onwards.
